data.description: This beautiful 1-story home located on the southeast side of San Antonio offers modern living in a historic area. The home opens up to a spacious living room which connects to the kitchen providing a great entertainment space. The three bedrooms offer comfortable accommodations including hardwood floors and great natural light. The backyard is fitted with a large covered patio great for entertainment or relaxation as well as a shed in the corner of the yard for extra space. Located within 5 minutes from southside Lions park east and 5 minutes from HWY 410 giving easy access to get to the rest of the city.
